Can anyone refer me to the source of the guidelines for removal of
accumulations of pigeon feces which I saw years ago (about 1993)? I had a
copy of the guidelines which were from an authoritative source which I
unfortunately do not remember. They essentially called for a moon-suit and
various other precautions. I now regret that I did not keep a copy, and I
am seeing this question arise with increasing frequency. Thanks to the
community for any assistance available!
